import React from "react";
import { Container, Grid, Typography,TextField, Button } from "@material-ui/core";

const Enterprise = ()=>{
    return(
        <Container>
                <Grid container spacing={2}>
                    <Grid item sm={12} >
                            <Typography> Datos de Empresa </Typography>
                    </Grid>
                    <Grid item sm={6}>
                         <TextField fullWidth id="outlined-basic" label="RUC" variant="outlined" />
                    </Grid>
                    <Grid item sm={6}>
                         <TextField fullWidth id="outlined-basic" label="Razón Social" variant="outlined" />
                    </Grid>
                    <Grid item sm={6}>
                         <TextField fullWidth id="outlined-basic" label="Nombre Comercial" variant="outlined" />
                    </Grid>
                    <Grid item sm={6}>
                         <TextField fullWidth id="outlined-basic" label="Dirección" variant="outlined" />
                    </Grid>
                    <Grid item sm={6}>
                         <TextField fullWidth id="outlined-basic" label="Sucursal" variant="outlined" />
                    </Grid>
                    <Grid item sm={12}>
                         <Button variant="contained" color="primary" >Guardar</Button>
                    </Grid>
                </Grid>
        </Container>
    );
}
export default Enterprise;
